<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Hermoupolis Magna</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀπολλώνιος Ἀπολλωνίωι τῶι 

    <lb n="2"/><choice><corr>τιμιωτάτωι</corr><sic>τιμωιτατωι</sic></choice> χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>γενόμενος ἐν Λύκων πόλει τῆι <num value="2">β</num> 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ λαβών σου τὰ ἐπιστόλια ἥσθην, 

    <lb n="5"/>ἄδελφε, ἐπὶ τῶι σε ἐρρῶσθαι μετὰ 

    <lb n="6"/>τῶν σῶν, τοῦτο γάρ μοι δι᾽ εὐχῆς 

    <lb n="7"/>ἐστιν. Πλουτίωνα παρεπιδημοῦν-

    <lb n="8"/>τα οὐχ εὗρον, λέγεται δὲ τὸ ἐντόλιόν 

    <lb n="9"/>σου ἀπηρτικέναι. τοῦτο οὖν εὐθέως, 

    <lb n="10"/>ἐὰν παραγένηται, ἀναπεμφθή-

    <lb n="11"/>σεταί σοι. περὶ δὲ τοῦ μὴ παραγεγε-

    <lb n="12"/>νῆσθαι <add place="supralinear"><handShift new="m2"/> με <choice><corr>πρὸς</corr><sic>πρως</sic></choice></add> <handShift new="m1"/> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">πρὸς</del> σὲ παρακαλῶ <choice><corr>συνγνῶ-

    <lb n="13"/>ναί</corr><sic>συνγνωιναι</sic></choice> μοι, τὰ γὰρ μετέωρα παρακατέ-

    <lb n="14"/>σχέ με. μεθ᾽ ἡμέρας δὲ ὀλίγας, ἐὰ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν οἱ</supplied> 

    <lb n="15"/>θεοὶ σώζωσι, παρέσομαι πρὸς σέ. 

    <lb n="16"/><handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι, 

    <lb n="17"/>κύριέ μου Ἀπολλώνιε, 

    <lb n="18"/>μετὰ τῶν ἀβασκάντων σου 

    <lb n="19"/>παιδίων. <handShift new="m3"/> ἔρρωσο. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="20"/><handShift new="m1"/> Ἀπολλωνίωι <expan>στρατη<ex cert="high">γῷ</ex></expan> <g type="x"/> <expan>Ἀπολλωνοπ<ex cert="high">ολίτου</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">Ἑπτα</ex></expan>κωμίας. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.19605" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.19605" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="0116" notAfter="0120">2. Hälfte 116 - 120 (?)</date></p></div><div n="meta.19605" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Gehört zum Archiv des Strategen Apollonios. Zur Datierung vgl. Kortus, Briefe, S. 15.</p></div><div n="meta.19605" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.19605" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Brem.</title><biblScope type="numbers">20</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">19605</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0083</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">20</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0083;;20" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.19605" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.19605" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="low" full="yes">Hermopolis</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>